# ABC081A - Placing Marbles

## 問題

<https://atcoder.jp/contests/abs/tasks/abc081_a>

## 回答1

```elixir
defmodule Main do
  def main do
    :stdio
    |> IO.read(:all)
    |> solve()
    |> IO.puts()
  end

  def solve(input) do
    input
    |> String.trim()
    |> String.codepoints()
    |> Enum.map(&String.to_integer/1)
    |> Enum.sum()
  end
end
```

```elixir
"""
101
"""
|> Main.solve()
|> then(&(&1 == 2))
```

```elixir
"""
000
"""
|> Main.solve()
|> then(&(&1 == 0))
```
